privateJob.title: Capgemini Notification 2021 – Openings for Various Project Executive Posts
privateJob.body:
Name of the post:

  • Project Manager

Description:

Capgemini has issued a notification to fill the vacancies of various posts of Project Manager. If you are finding jobs in Bangalore then feel free to apply online from The ProGrad .The candidates who are interested in the vacancies issued by Capgemini can see the detailed information about key skills required, educational qualification, total vacancies, how to apply, roles, and responsibilities are given below. If you are interested then read the details that are given below.

Total vacancies:

  • Various vacancies has released.

Selection Process:

  • Interview

Role and responsibility:

  • The role of the project manager is to manage client projects; Plan, coordinate, and ensure completion on schedule & within budget. In the context of cloud migrations, a project/program manager is responsible for Application / Server migrations
  • He / She needs to work with all required stakeholders to ensure successful migration of workloads from source to target environment [Public AWS, Azure & Google / Private Cloud]. Set deadlines, assign responsibilities, and monitor and summarize progress of the project

Application fee:

  • No information is given about the application required.

Educational qualification:

The candidates who are interested to apply for the Capgemini  job must have the following qualification:

  • The candidates must have completed the B.E, B.Tech, M.E/M.Tech from a recognized university to apply for the Capgemini Notification 2021

Key skills required :

The candidates who are interested to apply in these job openings must have the following key skills that are required to do this:

  • Strong Infrastructure project manager, preferably with cloud experience
  • Effective English Communication Verbal & Non-verbal
  • Strong working knowledge of project planning tools like MS Project, MS Excel, MS Powerpoint
  • Effective influencing and negotiating skills in an environment where this role may not directly control resources
  • Expertise in setting and managing customer expectations
  • Developing and Tracking Budgets and Financials

Payscale info. :

  • The Payscale information will be decided at the time of the interview.

The document needs to be carried:

The candidates who will be selected for the interview must carry the below-mentioned documents:

  • The first and foremost thing is your resume/CV which has your educational background and other related information.
  • You must have your Adhaar card for identity purposes.
  • You must have other identity proofs like a PAN card, voter id, or Passport to prove your citizenship.
  • At last, you should have photocopies of important educational certificates.

How to apply for Capgemini Notification 2021?

Candidates who are eligible and interested to apply for Capgemini  Job then you should follow the below steps to apply:

  • Note: You can also apply by clicking the apply now button shown above to apply directly from here
  • First of all, read the Capgemini notification thoroughly at the official website @capgemini.com.
  • You should have an email id and a phone number for communication purposes.
  • Click on the apply now link for the post you want to apply for.
  • Fill in the required details and submit.
  • Pay the application fee asked for.
  • Finally submit and download the application form for future purposes.
